Below is the change Apache Shiro 1.4.2 made to fix CVE-2019-12422. AesCipherService now defaults to AES in GCM mode — an authenticated encryption mode — instead of CBC:

**File: AesCipherService.java (Apache Shiro 1.4.2 — the fix relative to 1.4.1)**
